item.title: CVE-2017-11769|2024-09-16T21:08:58.639Z -- microsoft%20corporation -- microsoft%20windows%20trie
item.description: The Microsoft Windows TRIE component on Microsoft Windows 10 Gold, 1511, 1607, and 1703, and Windows Server 2016 allows a remote code execution vulnerability in the way it handles loading dll files, aka "TRIE Remote Code Execution Vulnerability".
